task.summary: ShowLookup looking up the Show Details on theTVDB
Fixed null pointer exception on special episodes
Lookup Episode information; added optino to provide a hit for shows with multiple matches.
Extracted Tag Parser to separate class and added tags from the extended information looked up from theTVDB.com
Fixed a couple bugs renaming shows.
Initial add of commercial detection, removal and transcoding using Comskip and ffmpeg
Added support for renaming show specials and handle shows without a specific episode title
Test resource for show without a episode title
Added keyword new keyword "{Series Name}" which will include the year if multiple shows with the same name exist.
Added a option to backup the original media before processing it with the Commercial Detector/Transcoding, etc.
Cache the retrieved theTVDb.com API key so we make fewer hits to the API.
Added an option to show what actions will be applied to media files and in which order
Fixed handling of quoted files names with spaces in them
